+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0
+ *
+ * Assembly level code for mshv_vtl VTL transition
+ *
+ * Copyright (c) 2025, Microsoft Corporation.
+ *
+ * Author:
+ *   Naman Jain <namjain@microsoft.com>
